QuestData.Title: Mysterious Greenery
QuestData.Description:
There's a bright power emanating from the place above. I'm drawn towards it, like a moth to a light!
I want to check it out, whatever it is. Won't you join me, please? It'll be so fun!
QuestData.LogDescription: Visit the Untamed Verdure with Glimmercane.
QuestData.RewardText:
We are Circle Koh of the jiro.
We are here to fix this land.
